  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink281-kilavi">āyattōṭu viḷaiyāṭṭu viruppiṉāl poḻilakam pukunta talaiviyai yetirppaṭṭ oḻukukiṉṟa talaimakaṉ avaḷ puṉaṅ kāvaṟk uriyaḷāy niṉṟatu kaṇṭu makiḻntu colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the hero, who kept encountering the heroine who had entered the grove desiring to play with her companions, said, rejoicing on seeing that she stood as one fit to guard the field.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink281">
<l>veḷḷa varampi ṉūḻi pōkiyuṅ</l>
<l>kiḷḷai vāḻiya palavē yoḷḷiḻai</l>
<l>yirumpal kūntaṟ koṭicci</l>
<l>peruntōṭ kāval kāṭṭiyavvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>May the parakeets live,</l> 
        <l>[even as] aeons pass beyond their vast limit—</l>
        <l rend="space">[for] they have shown her,</l>
        <l>the creeper-like girl</l>
        <l>with many dark tresses,</l>
        <l>she of big shoulders,</l>
        <l rend="space">to guard the millet fields.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
